Without a doubt, the best Dallas craft beer out there. Fantastic appearance and palate. Superb balance of malt and hops. Will even win over non- beer drinkers- the only time I have ever had someone say "I'll have what she's having". If you are in North Texas and you're not drinking this, you're missing out.

---Rated via Beer Buddy for iPhone

Strong burnt sugar notes. Touch of vanilla. Perfect texture. Hearty, welcoming smell. Absolutely fantastic. Definitely a favorite!
